node.text:
The one-of-a-kind @JacobandCo . Chiron Red and Black timeрiеce contains the in-house caliber JCAM37 manual winding movement that powers the clock, the tourbillon and the replica of the Bugatti "W16 engine" animation. Thе movement is оperated by the novel three- crown winding system. The first crown on the left sets the clock. The second stem winds both the clock and the engine animation. The third stem starts the on-demand engine animation. The watch is being sold exclusively through the Watches of Switzerland showroom in the Wynn Las Vegas resort. 

It started with an idea conceived by @JacobandCo . together with Bugatti - how to reproduce the visceral sensation of the iconic Bugatti 16-cylinder engine in a timepiece.

The Bugatti Chiron TourBillon from Jacob & Co. is a world-first - - a true engine on the wrist. 🔥

#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches #watch #watches #dailywatch #luxurywatch #luxurywatches #luxe #watchlover

node.text:
An Absolute Crazy Spec On This Bugatti Divo 😍🔥
Photo @keystothejungle 

#bugattidivo

Start Your Engines. @jacobandco 🔥

The BUGATTI Chiron Tourbillon recreates the famous BUGATTI W16 engine in a timepiece. Visible from the top and through the BUGATTI horseshoe grilI, the animation and the inclined tourbillon are perfectly positioned to share this amazing movement with your friends.

The @jacobandco . Bugatti Chiron timepieces come with an exclusive "Swiss" passport. This bright red official document, available in multiple languages, comes with a greeting from Jacob & Co. founder, Jacob Arabo, a certificate of authenticity, technical details, instructions on how to operate the watch, a "Swiss stamp" and most importantly, the Jacob & Co. stamp, allowing you to enter the world of audacious luxury "Inspired by the Impossible."

Isn’t that fascinating? 😍

#jacobandco #jacobandcowatches
#watches #watchesofinstagram #watch #luxurywatches #dailywatch #instawatch #luxe
